title: Rodeo champion Kelsie Domer’s 3 year old daughter Oaklynn dies after tragic horse accident during medical episode
summary_full: Rodeo champion Kelsie Domer’s 3 year old daughter Oaklynn died on February 19 after a horse suffered a medical episode and fell on them. Kelsie survived but Oaklynn did not. The news was shared through an obituary and reported by Rodeo Life. The rodeo community honored Oaklynn by wearing pink and sharing heartfelt tributes.
